From: Marcin FM <marcin@lgic.pl>
Subject: [PATCH] Drop benchmark-only criterion dependency

Criterion is used only by upstream benchmarks and is not needed to build or
test the protocol library for Fedora.

--- a/Cargo.toml
+++ b/Cargo.toml
@@ -47,3 +47,0 @@
-[dev-dependencies.criterion]
-version = "0.4"
-
